{"word":"G639 - ἀπορέω - aporéō - ap-or-eh'-o - Doubt","slug":"G639","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀπορέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>aporéō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>ap-or-eh'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Doubt"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03B1;&#x0313;&#x03C0;&#x03BF;&#x03C1;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03C9; - aporeo&#x0304;</b> - <i>ap-or-eh'-o</i><p/>From a compound of <a href=\"#/G1\">G1</a> (as a negative particle) and the base of <a href=\"#/G4198\">G4198</a>; to <i>have no way</i> out, that is, <i>be at a loss</i> (mentally): - (stand in) doubt, be perplexed."}]}